text: Muammar Zainal Abedin (, born June 14, 1954) sometimes shortened Muammar ZA or Muammar Z.A. is a popular senior Qari or Qur'an reciter and Hafiz from Indonesia well known nationally and internationally. == Other websites == * Category:1954 births Category:Islamic religious leaders Category:Living people Category:Indonesian Muslims Category:Quran reciters
